}
```

In this JSON output, the elements are components commonly used in scalable system architectures, particularly within the AWS Cloud Environment. Note that specific implementations can change based on cloud provider or on-premises setups, as well as needs for security, cost, type of workload, and other factors. The specifics would depend on additional requirements beyond the simple "Scalable system" provided.
